{"tid":853830,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"埃及球迷太可怕！金球獎民意調查 沙拿獲58%選票","createTime":"2018-10-09T02:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T09:17:54.000Z","uid":18669,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f14ee19f53e7d78c6313ea333b68fc2198c48c","tid":853830,"uid":18669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:06:36.000Z","msg":"昨晚，《法國足球》公佈了2018年金球獎30人候選名單，C朗、美斯、摩迪等巨星悉數入選。名單公佈後，《法國足球》做了一項民意調查，結果卻出乎意料。<br />\n<br />\n在&ldquo;你認為誰應該贏得2018年金球獎&rdquo;的投票中，得票最多的不是美C，也不是摩迪，而是埃及球星沙拿。他的得票率是驚人的58%，遠遠超過了其他29人。 。<br />\n<br />\n得票第二多的美斯，他的支持率是23%。被視為最大熱門的C朗和摩迪，在球迷票選中卻不太受待見，C朗僅獲得6%的選票，摩迪更是只有2%。"},{"pid":"3f341e4e6e6a351992ab549f9148e8152b1284e3","tid":853830,"uid":31314,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:08:29.000Z","msg":"好彩金球獎係記者投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b947db085818ee49e1dfb03daa0ab1c510cbe1b","tid":853830,"uid":19126,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:09:10.000Z","msg":"非洲佬可怕咋呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092d39a7def522adf891170fe983d9522e657199","tid":853830,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:10:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8be9b3cbb554899348ee99ace1c5dc105732f2ba","tid":853830,"uid":52571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:26:31.000Z","msg":"樓主又jer利狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d33caabb708aa4f531f32b6f7cf1b747e0ab07","tid":853830,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"8be9b3cbb554899348ee99ace1c5dc105732f2ba","tid":853830,"uid":52571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:26:31.000Z","msg":"樓主又jer利狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkg